1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:11,000
The errand robot tests whether the modules work together.

2
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:22,000
An errand is a sequence of grounded task models.

3
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:33,000
The humanoid body makes execution hardware-specific.

4
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:44,000
Recognition supplies objects, relations, and task cues.

5
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:55,000
Skill agents turn each task model into local action.

6
00:00:55,000 --> 00:01:07,000
System integration exposes the representation bottleneck.

7
00:01:07,000 --> 00:01:18,000
The next chapter asks what task essence really means.
